data.title: Asa National Quality Controllers: Updated On 09 July 2018
data.meta_description: ASA-National-Quality-Controllers-Updated-July-2018 - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or view presentation slides online. The document lists quality controllers for Athletics South Africa (ASA) including referees, route/course measurers, and equipment assizers as of July 9, 2018. It provides names, contact details, qualifications and areas of specialization for over 100 quality controllers broken down by province. The lists span pages 2 through 40 and include demographics for each individual.
